metadata.name: SAGACHA NO 1 - RADAR
metadata.description:
SAIGON'S CHARACTERS. 
" THIS PROJECT INCLUDES PHOTOGRAPHY AND VISUAL CHARACTERS, INSPIRED FROM THE CULTURAL DIFFERENCE, CLASSES, POPULATION,... OF  UNIQUE CITY IN VIETNAM- HO CHI MINH CITY (SAIGON)
IN MY FEELING, SAI GON HAS A TYPICAL SOUND: " XON XAO SAI GON"  FOR THIS PLACE: GROWTH AND SURPRISE.
THIS SOUND HAS POSITIVE AND NEGATIVE CHARACTERISTICS IN THE DEVELOPMENT OF CULTURAL, SOCIAL LIFE OF MODERN SAIGON.

MULTI-COLORS, IRREGULAR, COLLISION AND INTERTWINING, BUT FULL OF LIFE OF A POTENTIAL CITY IN ASIA - SAI GON - HO CHI MINH CITY"

SAIGON'S CHARACTERS NO.1 : RADAR
The character was created based on the inspiration of a street vendor hiding eyes and thoughts under a conical hat and layers of plastic.
